title: RED DRAGON Pegasus Professional Tungsten Steeltip Darts Set Available in 21, 23, 24, 25, 26, 28, 30 Gram with Flights, Stems (Shafts) and Wallet
features: PRECISION ENGINEERED TUNGSTEN DARTS: Experience unrivalled accuracy with Red Dragon's Pegasus tungsten dart set, designed for ultimate balance and control to elevate your professional darts performance.

VERSATILE WEIGHT OPTIONS: The Red Dragon Pegasus Series offers multiple weight options, including 21g, 22g, 23g, 24g, 25g, 26g, 28g, & 30g darts. Whether you prefer a light dart or a heavy dart, this darts set has options to suit any playing style.

AERODYNAMIC STEM & FLIGHT SYSTEM: Equipped with 2 x Red Dragon Dart Shafts, ensuring each dart maintains a stable and consistent trajectory. These darts also come with 2 x Standard shape Hardcore flights, offering superior lift and enhanced durability. Both the stems & flights come in black & white.

DURABLE CONSTRUCTION: Crafted with high-quality materials, these Red Dragon darts are built to withstand intense play, making them the perfect choice for professional darts enthusiasts. The set includes a premium carry case, making it easy to transport your darts wherever you play.

ERGONOMIC GRIP DESIGN: Enjoy enhanced control with the Red Dragon Pegasus darts, featuring an ergonomic grip that provides enhanced control and stability, reducing slippage and boosting confidence in every throw. Please Note: Packaging Designs May Vary.
